n1uppercaseecho222e36...Nodes and WorkersOckam Nodes run very lightweight, concurrent,and stateful actors called Ockam Workers.Using Ockam Routing, a node can deliver messagesfrom one worker to another local worker.Using Ockam Transports, nodes can also routemessages to workers on other remote nodes.In response to a message, a worker can makedecisions about what to do next:Change its internal state.Create more workers.Or send more messages, including replies.
